TITLE: Zod Schema Validation Integration with HeroUI
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates integration of Zod schema validation with HeroUI forms. Shows how to validate form data using Zod schemas and handle validation errors.
SOURCE: https://github.com/heroui-inc/heroui/blob/canary/apps/docs/content/docs/guide/forms.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import {z} from "zod";

const schema = z.object({
  name: z.string().min(1),
  age: z.coerce.number().positive(),
});

function handleRequest(formData: FormData) {
  const result = schema.safeParse(Object.fromEntries(formData));

  if (!result.success) {
    return {
      errors: result.error.flatten().fieldErrors,
    };
  }

  return {
    errors: {},
  };
}
```

