TITLE: Creating Controlled Forms with HeroUI Components
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates how to create a controlled form using HeroUI components and React's useState hook. It shows how to manage form state and handle value changes in real-time.
SOURCE: https://github.com/heroui-inc/heroui/blob/canary/apps/docs/content/docs/guide/forms.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
