TITLE: Real-time Password Validation with NextUI
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of real-time password validation using NextUI's Input component. Validates password length, uppercase letters, and symbol requirements as the user types.
SOURCE: https://github.com/heroui-inc/heroui/blob/canary/apps/docs/content/blog/v2.6.0.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: tsx
