TITLE: Configuring Client-Side Routing with NextUI Provider in Next.js Pages Router
DESCRIPTION: This code shows how to set up client-side routing in a Next.js app using the Pages Router. It configures the HeroUIProvider component in the _app.tsx file to enable client-side navigation for NextUI components.
