TITLE: Implementing Breaking Changes for Popover Component in JSX
DESCRIPTION: Migration example showing how to update Popover component styling from using dedicated arrow slots to using before pseudo-elements for arrow positioning. The content styling now applies directly to the content slot rather than the base slot.
