TITLE: Updating Vite Configuration for Tailwind v4 Integration
DESCRIPTION: Updates the Vite configuration to include the Tailwind v4 Vite plugin. Imports the @tailwindcss/vite plugin and adds it to the plugins array in the configuration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/heroui-inc/heroui/blob/canary/apps/docs/content/docs/guide/tailwind-v4.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: diff-js
CODE:
```
// vite.config.ts
import { defineConfig } from 'vite'
import react from '@vitejs/plugin-react'
import tsconfigPaths from 'vite-tsconfig-paths'
+ import tailwindcss from "@tailwindcss/vite"

export default defineConfig({
-  plugins: [react(), tsconfigPaths()],
+  plugins: [react(), tsconfigPaths(), tailwindcss()],
})
```

