DESCRIPTION: Code example showing how to update Select component's popover styling to use before pseudo-elements for arrow positioning and content slot for popover content styling, replacing the previous base and arrow slot approach.
SOURCE: https://github.com/heroui-inc/heroui/blob/canary/apps/docs/content/blog/v2.2.0.mdx#2025-04-20_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: diff-jsx
CODE:
```
 <Select
      items={users}
      label="Assigned to"
      className="max-w-xs"
      variant="bordered"
      popoverProps={{
        classNames: {
-          base: "p-0 border-small border-divider bg-background",
-          arrow: "bg-default-200",
+          base: "before:bg-default-200", // the before pseudo element controls the popover's arrow
+          content: "p-0 border-small border-divider bg-background", // now instead of the "base" slot we use the "content" slot
        },
      }}
    >
     ...
    </Select>
  );
}``;
```

